{
  "page": "Battle of the Borderland",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Battle of the Borderland</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Date</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_96_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">96&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\nVolantene defeat<br />Creation of the <a href=\"/index.php/Triarchy\" title=\"Triarchy\">Triarchy</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%; text-align:left;\">\n<tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Combatants</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantis</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\"><a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lys</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Myr\" title=\"Myr\">Myr</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Tyrosh\" title=\"Tyrosh\">Tyrosh</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Commanders</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">Unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      Unknown</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Strength</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">Unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      Unknown</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Casualties</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">Unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      Unknown</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>Battle of the Borderland</b> was a major battle involving four of the nine <a href=\"/index.php/Free_Cities\" title=\"Free Cities\">Free Cities</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_96_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">96&#160;AC</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_free_cities:_the_quarrelsome_daughters:_myr.2C_lys.2C_and_tyrosh.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_free_cities:_the_quarrelsome_daughters:_myr.2C_lys.2C_and_tyrosh.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lys</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Myr\" title=\"Myr\">Myr</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrosh\" title=\"Tyrosh\">Tyrosh</a> put their differences aside and made alliance to drove <a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantis</a> from the <a href=\"/index.php/Disputed_Lands\" title=\"Disputed Lands\">Disputed Lands</a>. The alliance defeated the Volantenes in the Battle of the Borderland.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Aftermath\">Aftermath</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Battle_of_the_Borderland&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Aftermath\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>After the battle, the three victorious cities forged an \"eternal alliance\", and formed a strong new power in Essos: the <a href=\"/index.php/Triarchy\" title=\"Triarchy\">Triarchy</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabheirs_of_the_dragon_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtrp.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtrp.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_viserys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_viserys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Battle_of_the_Borderland&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Triarchy\" title=\"Triarchy\">Triarchy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/War_for_the_Stepstones\" title=\"War for the Stepstones\">War for the Stepstones</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Daughters%27_War\" title=\"Daughters&#39; War\">Daughters' War</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Battle_of_the_Borderland&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"